*******************************************************************
* This is a description about "Tcpdump".                          *
* In case that u are required to use tcpdump to capture packages. *
*******************************************************************

capture original package datum, and write to A.pcap:
	- tcpdump -i athX -w A.pcap

capture the description of packages, and write to B.pcap:
	- tcpdump -i athX > B.pcap

